                  <paragraph>NDC 54868-5299-1<br/>Ten  (10)  10  mL  oral  liquid  unit  dose  cups  per  tray.<br/>Ten  (10)  trays  per  shipper.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>NDC 54868-5299-0<br/>Ten  (10)  10  mL  oral  liquid  unit  dose  cups  per  tray.<br/>Three  (3)  trays  per  shipper.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">SHAKE  WELL  BEFORE  USING</content>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20110401"/>
               <component>
                  <section>
                     <id root="c523733e-4cbd-4303-ba16-6e39485bd74f"/>
                     <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
                     <text>
                        <paragraph>Store  at  controlled  room  temperature  20-25°C  (68-77°F)  [see  USP]). Avoid  freezing.</paragraph>
                     </text>
                     <effectiveTime value="20101124"/>
                  </section>
